{"tid":115604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本植皮] 當日台灣八仙粉塵爆炸，日本無限量供應人工敷料幫手","createTime":"2017-02-10T16:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T02:19:03.000Z","uid":54684,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65c7fe1cc20af075e4943875e3e6ad7075022b19","tid":115604,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ftv.com.tw/newscontent.aspx?sno=2015703S03M1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ftv.com.tw%2Fnewscontent.aspx%3Fsno%3D2015703S03M1&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=bd57e57c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ftv.com.tw/newscontent.aspx?sno=2015703S03M1</a><br />\n八仙粉塵爆炸，震驚國際，4年前311地震，台灣援助日本，感念台灣的這一份情，日方特別派人在昨天（7月2日）來台，除了將提供人工皮，無限量供應的人工敷料，還有50床專供嚴重燒燙者使用的矽砂床，甚至是日方獨門的人工皮膚培植技術。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係想提下︰<br />\n香港有無拍得住日本既人工敷料/皮膚培植技術？<br />\n定係香港係咪夠哂人力物力幫D傷者好好處理佢地D皮膚？<br />\n好多都重係女士<br />\n唔想佢地就咁就一世  佢地會好難接受<br />\n<br />\n利申︰希望學生妹傷勢不太嚴重  無論如何  早日康復"},{"pid":"3bb3865593ed833480d273eeb63c7d3837523dbc","tid":115604,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c567a0f346a1a54eeafde2f410a439cb7588acc0","tid":115604,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"香港人話晒都有捐過錢嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63654ce5cd1ca8a5bac26b75e2a3337efcf75c2","tid":115604,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"如果有需要 我第一個捐錢"},{"pid":"4a108933b69256650a59cf1b0af076634b002ae9","tid":115604,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"錢其實政府實有<br />\n<br />\n只係唔知香港醫療水平去到點<br />\n<br />\n夠唔夠handle呢D傷者既皮膚問題"},{"pid":"1ee2d2e68f8c7e02a940ee282759cf2eb18b4c6d","tid":115604,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢其實